职位描述
Job Description 岗位职责:
1.Responsible for testing process optimization to improve the OEE and minimums the production losses;
负责测试工艺的优化，提升设备的整体效率，降低生产损失；
2.Responsible for maintaining and optimizing the test plan, analyzing the test result to improve the cycle time and FPY;
负责维护和优化测试计划，分析测试结果，制定改善措施来降低节拍和提高通过率；
3.Support internal and CCC, CIQ, VDE audit, organize the annual calibration of the test equipment and instrument;
支持质量内审和外审，组织设备和仪器的年度校验；
4.In charge of the work station design and process setup at responsible area;
负责所负责区域的岗位规划和工艺设置；
5.Responsible for creation of process documents: work instructions, use manual, process flow chart, control plans, AM/PM plan etc.;
负责工艺文件的编写：操作说明， 使用手册，工艺流程图，控制计划，维护计划等；
6.Support new product project, ECO projects, and productivity improvement project;
支持新产品导入项目，工程变更项目和生产效率改善项目等；
7.Cooperate with the equipment supplier to support the new installations or modifications, organize necessary test to prove the capability of the equipment;
与供应商合作支持新设备的安装或改造，并组织必要的测试以证明设备的性能是否达到要求；
8.Support new equipment, new tools pre-acceptance at supplier site and later installation coordination at BSH, performing the test and follow up the final acceptance；
负责新设备、新模具的预验收，总协调后期的安装并及时的跟进设备的最终验收事宜;
9.Support troubleshoot in the production line and able to lead the problem solving from technical perspective;
支持生产线的故障排除，并能主导技术问题的解决;

Professional Requirements 专业资质要求:
1.Has rich automation knowledge and implement experience, robot vision application experience is preferred;
具有丰富的自动化知识和应用经验，有机器人视觉应用经验者优先；
2.Good English level in both oral and written;
良好的英语听说读写能力；
3.Has strong logical thinking and analytical skills, willing to learn new technology;
有很强的逻辑思维和分析能力，愿意去学习新知识新技术；
4.Familiar with database software applications such as SQL or Oracle;
熟悉SQL或者Oracle 等数据库软件应用；
5.Be skilled with lean production tools, SPC, and other IE methodology;
熟练运用精益工具，SPC过程控制及其它工业工程方法；
6.Be familiar with quality tools, 6sigma, 8D, FMEA;
熟悉质量工具， 六西格玛， 8D和失效模式分析等；
7.Good communication and coordination skills, strong team spirit and self-responsible and working independently;
良好的沟通协调能力，很强的团队合作精神, 有责任心，能独立工作；
8.Major in electrical engineering and automation or automation
电气工程及其自动化或者自动化等专业
